com.scalar.dl.ledger.model

Class ContractExecutionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scalar.dl.ledger.model.ContractExecutionResult

  • @Immutable
public class ContractExecutionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The result of contract execution. It contains the result of the contract execution along with a list of AssetProofs from Ledger and Auditor.
